[Issue]: Magic numbers used in conditionals.
[Impact]: Hard to understand the business logic. Changing the value requires hunting down all occurrences.
[Fix (Code Diff)]:
```typescript
const STATUS_ACTIVE = 2;
const MIN_AGE = 18;
if (user.status === STATUS_ACTIVE && user.age > MIN_AGE) {
    grantAccess(user);
}
```

Please review this diff:
+ public void pingIP(String ip) throws Exception {
+     Runtime.getRuntime().exec("ping -c 1 " + ip);
+ }

[Issue]: Command Injection via Runtime.exec().
[Impact]: Attacker can execute arbitrary system commands on the host server.
[Fix (Code Diff)]:
```java
public void pingIP(String ip) throws Exception {
    new ProcessBuilder("ping", "-c", "1", ip).start();
}
```

